Document: PortableCompressedTexture2D
Path: godot/classes/class_portablecompressedtexture2d.rst
Summary: Defines a compressed texture that can be loaded on different platforms.

PortableCompressedTexture2D

Inherits: Texture2D < Texture < Resource < RefCounted

A compressed texture that can be loaded on different platforms. This is useful for distributing compressed textures without needing to worry about the specific compression format supported by each platform.

This texture format is designed to be portable across different platforms and architectures. It stores the texture data in a compressed format that can be decompressed at runtime.

Key Rule: The primary purpose of PortableCompressedTexture2D is to ensure texture compatibility across diverse hardware and operating system combinations, avoiding platform-specific compression artifacts or loading failures.
